      "text": "File Metadata\n- FileId\n- File Name\n- MimeType\n- Size\n- OwnerId\n- S3Link\n- Creation Timestamp\n- Update Timestamp\n- Status: 'started'\n- Chunks: [\n    {\n        id as fingerprint,\n        status,\n        s3Link\n    }\n]",
