      "text": "Functional Requirements\n- upload a file\n- download a file\n- automatically sync files across devices\n\nOut of Scope\n- roll own blob storage\n\nNon-functional requirements\n- availability >> consistency\n- low latency upload and downloads\n- support large files <=50GB\n    - resumable uploads\n- high data integrity during sync -> sync accuracy\n\n- Observability\n- Safety\n- Auditability\n- Performant\n\n\nCore Entities\n- file (raw bytes)\n- File Metadata\n- Users\n\nAPI\n- POST /files -> 201\n{file, fileMetadata}\n\n- GET /files/:fileId -> File & FileMetadata\n\n- GET /changes?since ={timestamp} -> fileIds[]",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
